methods for mongodb operations from node
----------------------------------------------------
1.create - c- new modelname({key:value})
                                new users({
                                     acno:Number,
                                    uname:String,
                                    pws:String,
                                    balance:Number,
                                    transaction:[]
                                })
                                -save()

2.read - r -find() -> to access all datas from collection
    to read single data from collection use findone() method
    - findone({data}) eg: findone({accno:1000})
    - findone() use cheyyumbo argument aayii oru object kudii kodukkanam.
    - to find which data or whose data pass a parameter as object in findone() method.
3.update -u- findone({})
            - in update also findone() method use cheyyamm
4.delete-d - deleteone({})